name: OUTSKIRTS | Solaria Sentinel-T
description:
3200x3200

OUTSKIRTS could be called the evolution from the SPACER COLONIES series. We venture further into the galaxy until we reach the outskirts, where humans and animals in absence of order and control brought forth the most mysterious specimens and characters. It'll be a much smaller number of pieces, more free and abstract but with a clearer color palette that holds them together.
